---
title: Carb Smart Chicken and Feta Bunless Burgers with Greek-Style Salad
description: This dish has all the flavours of a Greek gyro without the bulky pita! Ground chicken seasoned parsley tops a Greek-style salad. A salty sprinkle of feta cheese and zippy parsley tzatziki finish off this zesty dinner.
